@NODE Connect "Connect.Guide: Short description"
One click on the Icon of Connect es it runs quiet in the Background. In the
WaitStatus it uses no CPU-Time. You can quit Connect, when you start it
again, with Exchange or the Workbench Command BREAK.
@ENDNODE



